query:
INSERT INTO bookmarks (
                user_id,
                created_at,
                modified_at,
                accessed_at,
                url,
                title,
                description,
                website_title,
                website_description,
                unread,
                shared,
                notes,
                import_properties
              ) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)
              RETURNING bookmark_id;
